      "date": "2012-01-03 22:48:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux release/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/3c928a5e-365c-11e1-8164-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
